https://developer.android.com/studio/
Download from browser
Then extract from download location and open terminal

Goto the location of bin folder the u will find studio.sh from location /download/filename/bin

sudo chmod 777 -R studio.sh  hit enter
then 
./studio.sh hit enter


if you will get this error then open new terminal from bin

Error:Unable to run mksdcard SDK tool in ubuntu
sudo apt-get install lib32z1 lib32ncurses5 lib32bz2-1.0 lib32stdc++6





